Pairing a service is really simple!
To begin, start the pairing process from the website you want to pair
The service website will ask for the pairing code that Latch generated on your device
For security reasons, the code will expire in 1 minute
If the time expires, tap the button to generate a new code
Once the pairing is confirmed, you can set up the service protection options

To prevent any unauthorized use, Latch gives you the control to lock your services with a single tap when you aren't using them.
Simple. Security and control with a single tap."
